  {
    "id": "cults-002",
    "target_worldview": "cults",
    "topic_zh": "摩门教：另一本经典与另一个福音",
    "topic_en": "Mormonism: Another Scripture and Another Gospel",
    "core_argument_zh": "摩门教（耶稣基督后期圣徒教会）在核心教义上与正统基督教存在根本分歧：（1）上帝曾经是另一个星球上的凡人，通过进步成为神（Lorenzo Snow信条\"人可以成为上帝\"）；（2）耶稣是灵世界中众多灵子女之一，与撒旦是\"灵兄弟\"；（3）《摩门经》和后来的启示被置于与圣经同等甚至更高的权威地位。\n\n摩门教的上帝观与圣经直接冲突。圣经教导上帝是从亘古到永远的（诗篇90:2），是不改变的（玛拉基书3:6），是唯一的真神（以赛亚书44:6\"除我以外再没有真神\"）。一位从凡人进化而来的上帝完全不是圣经所启示的上帝。\n\n考古学和语言学也对《摩门经》的可信度提出严重质疑。《摩门经》描述古代美洲有先进的基督教文明，使用钢铁、战马和象形文字——但考古学没有发现任何支持这些描述的证据。美洲原住民的DNA研究也不支持他们来自以色列的说法。\n\n此外，约瑟·斯密的亚伯拉罕书被证明是普通的埃及丧葬文献（呼吸许可书），而非他声称的亚伯拉罕亲笔写的记录。多位埃及学家独立确认了这一点，严重质疑了斯密的翻译能力和先知宣称。",
    "core_argument_en": "Mormonism (LDS Church) fundamentally diverges from orthodox Christianity: (1) God was once a mortal man on another planet who progressed to godhood (Lorenzo Snow couplet: 'As man is, God once was'); (2) Jesus is one of many spirit children in the pre-existence, a 'spirit brother' of Satan; (3) The Book of Mormon and later revelations are placed at equal or higher authority than the Bible.\n\nMormon theology directly conflicts with Scripture. The Bible teaches God is from everlasting to everlasting (Psalm 90:2), unchanging (Malachi 3:6), the only true God (Isaiah 44:6 'besides me there is no God'). A God who evolved from a mortal is utterly foreign to biblical revelation.\n\nArchaeology and linguistics also raise serious questions about the Book of Mormon's credibility. It describes advanced Christian civilizations in ancient America using steel, war horses, and hieroglyphics — but archaeology has found zero evidence supporting these descriptions. DNA studies of Native Americans also don't support Israelite origin claims.\n\nFurthermore, Joseph Smith's Book of Abraham was proven to be an ordinary Egyptian funerary document (Breathing Permit of Hôr), not Abraham's personal record as claimed. Multiple Egyptologists independently confirmed this, severely challenging Smith's translation ability and prophetic claims.",
    "common_objections": [
      {
        "objection_zh": "摩门教徒生活道德高尚，家庭重视，这不就证明它是好的吗？",
        "objection_en": "Mormons live moral lives and value family — doesn't that prove it's good?",
        "response_zh": "道德生活和家庭价值值得尊重，但真理不是由道德表现来决定的。许多宗教的信徒都生活得很好。核心问题是：这个信仰系统教导的关于上帝、基督和救恩的内容是否为真？耶稣警告说会有人奉祂的名行许多善事，但祂会说“我从来不认识你们“（马太福音7:22-23）。信仰的核心是真理，不仅仅是行为。",
        "response_en": "Moral living and family values deserve respect, but truth is not determined by moral performance. Adherents of many religions live admirable lives. The core question is: Are this system's teachings about God, Christ, and salvation TRUE? Jesus warned that some will do many good deeds in His name, yet He will say, 'I never knew you' (Matthew 7:22-23). The core of faith is truth, not merely behavior."
      },
      {
