        "response_zh": "撒旦“装作光明的天使“（哥林多后书11:14）。识别异端不看表面的热心，而看核心教义：（1）是否承认圣经是唯一最高权威？（2）是否承认基督的独一性？（3）是否教导唯独因信称义？（4）是否有圣经之外的“新启示“凌驾于圣经之上？全能神教会把《话在肉身显现》置于圣经之上，这是致命的偏离。",
        "response_en": "Satan 'disguises himself as an angel of light' (2 Corinthians 11:14). Identifying heresy requires examining core doctrine, not surface zeal: (1) Is the Bible the sole supreme authority? (2) Is Christ's uniqueness affirmed? (3) Is justification by faith alone taught? (4) Is there 'new revelation' placed above Scripture? CAG elevates 'The Word Appears in the Flesh' above the Bible — a fatal departure."
