        "response_zh": "新约抄本的关键优势不仅是数量，更是多样性。这些抄本来自不同的地理区域（埃及、叙利亚、北非、欧洲）、不同的抄写传统、不同的时间段。如果只是一个错误被反复复制，我们会看到所有抄本包含相同的错误。但实际情况是，通过比较不同传统的抄本，文本批评学家能够精确识别和排除抄写错误。这正是文本批评学（textual criticism）的方法论优势，而新约拥有的抄本多样性为这一方法提供了最佳条件。",
        "response_en": "The NT manuscripts' key advantage is not just quantity but diversity. They come from different geographical regions (Egypt, Syria, North Africa, Europe), different scribal traditions, and different time periods. If the same error were simply repeated, all manuscripts would contain identical mistakes. Instead, by comparing manuscripts across traditions, textual critics can precisely identify and eliminate copying errors. This is the methodological advantage of textual criticism, and the NT's manuscript diversity provides optimal conditions for it."
