        "response_en": "This is an unproven philosophical assumption, not a scientific conclusion. Neuroscientist Mario Beauregard notes abundant neuroscience evidence (placebo effects, meditation altering brain structure) showing top-down mental causation on the brain, incompatible with a purely computational model. Intentionality, qualia, and free will cannot be reduced to computation."
